WEBVTT

00:00:57.689 --> 00:01:00.252
by the man who I thought was my soulmate,

00:01:00.252 --> 00:01:03.737
many, many times.

00:01:03.737 --> 00:01:07.297
The man who I loved more than anybody on Earth

00:01:07.297 --> 00:01:11.376
held a gun to my head and threatened to kill me

00:01:11.376 --> 00:01:14.561
more times than I can even remember.

00:01:14.561 --> 00:01:17.304
I'm here to tell you the story of crazy love,

00:01:17.304 --> 00:01:20.488
a psychological trap disguised as love,

00:01:20.488 --> 00:01:23.340
one that millions of women and even a few men

00:01:23.340 --> 00:01:25.721
fall into every year.

00:01:25.721 --> 00:01:28.470
It may even be your story.

00:01:28.470 --> 00:01:31.513
I don't look like a typical domestic violence survivor.